Class TypeLibrary<T extends ReflectableType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.smudgr.app.project.reflect.ReflectionLibrary<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The ReflectableType this Library should manage

    public class TypeLibrary<T extends ReflectableType>
extends ReflectionLibrary<T>
    A TypeLibrary provides the ability to detect and organize all loaded concrete implementations of a given ReflectableType
